          <head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-334-24XA-headnote-1">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-334-24XA-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-334-24XA-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">All our Advices from <hi rend="italics">Dublin</hi> agree that Mr. <hi rend="italics">Wood's</hi> Copper Money has raised a general Ferment and Discontent in <hi rend="italics">Ireland</hi>; of which the two following Pieces. printed here are Authentick instances. The first is as follows.</l>
            </lg>
