            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-334-24XA-line-109" n="109"><lb/>Hear one Story more, and then I will stop:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-24XA-line-110" n="110">I dreamt, <hi rend="italics">Wood</hi> was told he should Die by a <hi rend="italics">Drop</hi>;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-24XA-line-111" n="111">So methought, he resolv'd no Liquor to taste,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-24XA-line-112" n="112">For fear the <hi rend="italics">First-Drop</hi> might as well be his <hi rend="italics">Last</hi>:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-24XA-line-113" n="113">But <hi rend="italics">Dreams</hi> are like <hi rend="italics">Oracles</hi>, 'tis hard to explain' em,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-24XA-line-114" n="114">For it prov'd that he dy'd of a <hi rend="italics">Drop</hi> at <note place="foot">·<hi rend="italics">Their Place of Execution like </hi>Tyburn<hi rend="italics"> near</hi> London.</note> <hi rend="italics">Killmanham</hi>:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-24XA-line-115" n="115">I wak'd with Delight, and not without Hope,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-24XA-line-116" n="116">Very soon to see <hi rend="italics">Wood, Drop</hi> down from a <hi rend="italics">Rope</hi>.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-24XA-line-117" n="117">How he and how we at each other should grin!</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-24XA-line-118" n="118">'Tis Kindness to hold a Friend up by the Chin;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-24XA-line-119" n="119">But soft, says the Herald, I cannot agree;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-24XA-line-120" n="120">For <hi rend="italics">Metal on Metal is false Heraldry</hi>:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-24XA-line-121" n="121">Why that may be true, yet <hi rend="italics">Wood</hi> upon <hi rend="italics">Wood</hi>,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-334-24XA-line-122" n="122">I'll maintain with my Life, is <hi rend="italics">Heraldry</hi> Good.</l>
          </lg>
